wikipedia_page.main: Kashy Keegan (born Matthew Kashy Keegan; 18 July 1983) is a British singer-songwriter. His song "This Is My Dream" has been described as an anthem for overcoming adversity.

response: * Kashy Keegan, singer-songwriter, was born in Worthing in 1983.
